name: Golven /weɪvz/
description: "Emotions are much like waves. We can’t stop them from coming, but we can choose which one to surf. To be entirely honest, you never really know what’s coming. A small wave, or maybe a big one. All you can really do is hope that when it comes, you can surf over it, instead of drown in its monstrosity" by @Baimtje
